Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:10.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,== srt字幕转制 ==
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:21.45,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,一八一七年九月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:24.45,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,巴黎年轻有为的诗人保罗魏尔伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:27.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,收到一封署名为蓝波
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,寄来的八首奇特的诗篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:30.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,作者署名：蓝波
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他立即回信道：
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,“亲爱的伟大灵魂\N来我们这儿吧，期待你”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:38.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,以下故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:42.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,直接源自他们的书信和诗篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:44.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,魏尔伦是大诗人之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:45.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,蓝波是个革命性的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:47.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他16岁到19岁的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:51.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,永远改变了现代诗的面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:18.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,主演：莱昂纳多.迪卡普里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:22.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,主演：戴维.休利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:26.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,主演：罗曼娜.波林热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:21.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,导演：阿涅斯卡.霍兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有时他用多愁善感的语调   \N  Sometimes he speaks in a kind of tender dialect
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,述说引人悔恨的死亡\Nof the death which causes repentance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:20.63,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,述说活着的忧伤人群 \N of the unhappy men who certainly exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,述说悲伤世事，生死离别 \N of painful tasks and heartrending departures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,In the hovels where we got drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,15,15,,在我们喝得酩酊大醉的简陋小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他泪眼观望围绕在身旁的\N he wept looking at those who surrounded us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,a cattle of poverty.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,15,0,15,,那些没用的贫苦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他在乱街扶起醉鬼 \N He lifted up drunks in the black streets.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.45,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他同情惨遭恶母虐待的孩子\N He had the pity a bad mother has for small children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:45.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他的动作如教义课上的女孩那般优雅 \N He moved with the graceof a little girl at catechism.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.74,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他假装通晓一切\N He pretended to know about everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:52.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,商业、艺术、医学\N business, art, medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我追随他 \N I followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我必须如此 \NI had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,先生，有人找你，在那边 \N Someone for you, sir. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我认识她吗？\NDo I know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.15,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她有名片给我\NShe gave me her card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,伊莎蓓·兰波 \N Isabella Rimbaud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请…\NPlease...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请坐 \NPlease sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,安迪一直在照顾你吧？ \NHas Andre been looking after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,喝点什么吗？\NCan I get you something to drink?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不用，谢谢\NNo, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请坐\N Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这真的是只是公事公办\N It's really a business matter...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想和你谈谈\NI want to discuss with you, Mr. Verlaine.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.37,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是几个月前出版的\NThis was published a few months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:21.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,完全未经授权的家兄的诗集\Na completely unauthorized selection of my brother's poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:26.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,家母和我想杜绝这类事情再发生\NMy mother and I are anxious to prevent anything like this from happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们想也许你可以帮忙\NWe thought you might be able to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.35,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,I? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.35,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,我？怎么帮？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:35.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我知道你存有家兄的很多手稿 \N I understand you have a large number of my brother's manuscripts.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我是有一些，没错 \N I have some, yes.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如蒙归还 \NWell, my mother and I would be very grateful...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,家母与我不胜感激\N if you would return them.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我总是……极其谨慎地\N I've always tried to use the utmost discretion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,处理关于令兄的事 \N in everything concerning your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,可以说我一直都在维护他的利益  \NI think I can say I've always defended his interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,说来也怪\NSometimes I wonder why, since in many ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为那在很多方面都跟我的利益相冲突\Nthey're diametrically opposed to my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:05:59.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不明白\NI don't see how.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,许多年后世人才理解令兄的作品\N It took many years for your brother's work to be understood...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,一旦他成名\Nbut once his name began to be known...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.80,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们的那一套便气数殆尽\Nit soon became clear that our ways were numbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,单凭旧体诗的音乐性已远远不够 \N The music of old-fashioned verse was no longer enough.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他把我们扫地出门\NHe swept us away.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我并不介意，你明白么？\NNot that I mind, you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:22.80,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我知道我也曾经是个好作家\N I know I was once a good writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不知道他这么出名 \N I didn't know his name was so well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:31.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如今年轻一代了解他 \NYes. The young understand him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:35.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他是未来之声\NHe's the voice of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.37,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对我来说最重要的 \NWhat matters to me most...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:44.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是我们合创最佳作品 \Nis that we did our best work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们两人\N Both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:57.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,巴黎，1871年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,早上好\NMorning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,, 我来找保罗魏尔伦 \NI'm looking for Paul Verlaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你是兰波先生吗？ \NAre you Monsieur Rimbaud?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,魏尔伦没跟你一起回来？\N Monsieur Verlaine is not with you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:16.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他去车站接你\NHe went to the station to meet you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他不知道我的长相\N He doesn't know what I look like, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我是傅勒维夫人\N I am Mrs. Maute de Fleurville...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,魏尔伦的岳母\NMonsieur Verlaine's mother-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是我女儿，魏尔伦夫人 \Nand this is my daughter...Mrs. Verlaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你从车站怎么来的？\N How did you get from the station?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:44.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,走路来的\NWalked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,要梳洗一下吗？\N Perhaps you'd like a wash.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:52.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不用 \NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你比我们想的还年轻\NYou're even younger than we imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你多大了？\NHow old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:01.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,亲爱的，问人年龄不礼貌\N Darling, it's not polite to ask people their ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我要小便\NI need a piss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,若不介意，请问你多大了？\NHow old are you, if you don't mind my asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.61,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他介意\NHe does.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,16岁\NSixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你在信上写21岁\NOnly you did say in your letter you were twenty-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:17.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,唔\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,I noticed you at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,10,15,,在火车站的时候我注意到你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不过我没想到那就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,彼此彼此\N Likewise.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你寄给我的那些诗\NThose poems you sent me...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:30.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,以21岁而言，真了不起\Nwere remarkable for someone of twenty-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对于一个16岁的人来说 更是史无前例\N For someone of sixteen , they're unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,所以我才自称21岁\NThat's why I told you I was twenty-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:41.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不想让你还没读诗就先觉得屈尊了\NI didn't want you to feel patronizing before you'd read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,当然\N Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但愿令堂没有太生我的气\N I hope your mother isn't too angry with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:47.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有\N No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,当她知道是你出旅费的时候看起来挺高兴 \NOnce she'd found out you'd sent the fare she seemed quite happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:06.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Monsieur Rimbaud? Charleville?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:06.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你是来自亚耳宁么，蓝波先生？查理维镇？\NYou... You come from the Ardennes, don't you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是个怡人的小镇吧？\NPleasant town, Charleville, isn't it?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,最烂的地方\NLast place on God's earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:15.13,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,令尊是做什么的？\Nand what does your father do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.42,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,想必是在喝酒\NDrinks mostly, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们十年没见过他了\NWe haven't seen him for ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不必，走了对他也好\NNo need to be. He's very well out of it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:30.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,晚餐后请你朗诗\NPerhaps you'd like to read something to us after dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不行\NNo. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- Why not?    - I Don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(360,440)}- 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(469,440)}- 我不想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我从不朗读我的诗\NI never read out my poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别的诗人都朗读他们的诗\NAll the other poets do.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别人怎么样我没兴趣\NI'm not interested in what all the other poets do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们有聚会\NWe have soirees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:48.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你不认为诗人可以互相学习么？\NDon't you think poets can learn from one another?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.13,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只有那些烂诗人才会\NOnly if they're bad poets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你知道这是什么么？\NYou know about this?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我知道是什么\NI know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是诗人的第三只眼\NIt's the poet's third eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,它能融化冰河\NMelts glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你认为我太太如何？\NWhat do you think of my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.12,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你认为呢？\NWhat do you think of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她还是只是个孩子\NShe's still only a child, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我也是啊\NSo am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,苦艾酒，两杯\NAbsinthe, two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你应该为出书做准备\NYou should do something about getting it published.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:48.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,为什么？作家都要出书\NWhy? Because that's what writers do.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:55.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我毫不在乎出书\NI couldn't care less about being published.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,最重要的是写作本身\NThe only thing that matters is the writing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,其余都是文学\NEverything else is literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.40,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,, {\pos(435,470)}- Your last book...   - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.40,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(388,440)}- 你最新一本书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.40,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(568,440)}- 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不够好\Nwasn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.45,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你认为不好？\NYou don't think so?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:07.15,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,婚前的垃圾\NPremarital garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不对，是情诗\NNo. Love poems.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:11.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,很多人觉得很美\NA lot of people found them very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,满纸的谎言\NBut they're all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:16.13,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不是谎言，我爱她\NThey're not lies. I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:19.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 爱？  - 对\N- Love?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(440,470)}- No such thing.    - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(430,440)}- 没那回事     - 什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,将家人和夫妻连在一起的\NWhatever it is binds families and married couples together...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,并不是爱\Nthat's not love.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:30.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是愚笨、 自私或恐惧\NThat's stupidity or selfishness or fear.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,爱不存在\NLove doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你错了\NYou're wrong.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那是利己主义\NSelf-interest exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,植根于自身利益的依恋\NAttachment based on personal gain exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,或是自我满足\NComplacency exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:46.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但爱不存在\NBut not love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:53.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,爱必须重新创造\NLove has to be reinvented.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:56.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他为何这么想逃避现实？\NWhy did he want so much to escape from reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,从未有人抱持这种目标\NThere never was a man with such an aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:05.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,也许他知道改变生命的秘密？\NDid he perhaps know secrets to change life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,"有时我见到了\N"Sometimes I've seen...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:12.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,人们自以为所见的"\N"what people think they've seen."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:20.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他跟我想像的不同\NHe's not how I imagined him.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:25.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,“我流太多的泪\N"I've wept too many tears...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:29.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,心碎的黎明”\N"heartbreaking dawns."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我比较喜欢你的诗\NI prefer your poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:39.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不大看得懂那种东西\NI don't really understand that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不，这是新诗\NNo. This is something new.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,“我已流太多泪”\N"I've wept too many tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:58.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,“心碎的黎明”\N"heartbreaking dawns."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,怎么了？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他在踢\NHe's kicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:17.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你看？\NYou see?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这里，及这里\NThere, there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:42.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你不觉得让他在你的朋友那住些日子会更好一些吗\NDon't you think it would be more sensible to get one of your friends to put him up for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.80,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别人都不理解他\NPeople don't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只有我能\NI'm the only one who understands him.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:01.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,父亲显然不会理解他\NWell, Daddy certainly won't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:08.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,看来你还没意识到，今年我支持这场革命\NYou don't seem to realise, we had a revolution this year which I supported.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.40,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我可能会丧命\NI could have been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.40,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如果我没有丢了工作\NIf I hadn't been thrown out of my job...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:16.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就算是只有一秒钟，难道你以为我会接受你父亲他妈的施舍么？\Nyou think I would have accepted your father's damn charity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:39.31,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不过是帮助一位朋友\NFor God's sake, all I'm doing is helping a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:44.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,为什么我们一定要遭受这种待遇？我可是你丈夫！\NWhy do we go through all this? I'm your husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对不起，保罗\NI'm sorry, Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你是想惹我发火？\NAre you trying to annoy me?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我没有\NNo.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那就别\NWell, don't.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,晚安，大家都睡了\NEvening! Everyone's in bed, I'm afraid...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,还是你是来找那个老家伙的？ \Nunless you've come to see the old boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,The old boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,那个老家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:46.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就是莫德傅勒维，你不是他的朋友吧？\NMaute de Fleurville, Not a friend of his, are you?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:51.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有没有兴趣买个十字架？\NYou wouldn't like to buy a crucifix, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我会以最合理的价钱卖给你\NI can let you have this one on extremely reasonable terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我看是真珍珠做的\NIt's made with real pearls, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你他妈的到底是谁？\NWho the hell are you?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我也想问你这个问题\NI might ask you the same question...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.35,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如果不是我够礼貌的话\NExcept I'd be more polite.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我就是莫德傅勒维\NI am Maute de Fleurville.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:08.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,啊\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:18.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是我打碎了的你的狗狗\NThen this is your dog I just broke.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:26.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,狗都是自由主义者\NDogs are all liberals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:37.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么时候你能不经我的允许\NSince when have you had the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:42.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就请人住到家里了？\Nto invite people to stay in this house without my permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:47.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如果我连在自己家里招待客人的权利都没有\NIf I can't put up a guest in my own home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那我宁愿住到别处去\Nwhen I feel like it, I might as well live somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如果你不是成天游游荡荡 你就可以租得起房子\NIf you weren't so idle, you might be able to afford to.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:56.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 你很清楚自从社区    - 别找藉口\N- You know very well since the Commune...  - Any excuse.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你也不见得就多努力工作\NI don't notice you working your fingers to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:01.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你再碰到那个小混混时\NWhen you next see that hooligan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:05.29,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请他归还他偷走的东西\Nyou'll kindly ask him to return the objects he's pilfered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:09.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 你在说什么？  - 他会明白我的意思的\N- What are you talking about?  - He'll know what I mean.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.12,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那你就自己去说\NThen ask him yourself.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我很乐意告诉你，他已经走了\NI'm happy to say, he's left the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,23,0,15,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,谢天谢地\NThank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我以为再也找不到你\NI thought I was never going to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不知道那老家伙捣什么鬼\N I don't know what that bastard thought he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 那是他的家    - 是的\N- It's his house.    - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,走\N Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我给你找个地方\NWe'll find you somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,来呀 \NCome on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.38,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,恐怕只有这样了\NIt's not much, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:53.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- Just for a few days.    - It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:53.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 反正就待几天    - 这儿很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你爱她吗？\NSo do you love her?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:03.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,当然，她十全十美\NOf course. She's ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:08.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,18岁，漂亮、有钱\NEighteen, beautiful, plenty of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,贤惠，怀上了我的孩子\Nall the wifely virtues. And she's about to give me a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你们有共同点吗？\NDo you have anything in common?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她聪明吗？\NIs she intelligent?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她能理解你吗？\NDoes she understand you?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不能\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那她唯一能带给你的就是性\NThen the only thing she can give you is sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,保罗，保罗 \NPaul , Paul
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,1,0,15,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,1,15,,嗨！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.74,微软雅黑0 1 30,,1,0,15,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.74,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,1,15,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,找到他了吗？\NDid you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,找到了\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:22.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那他还给你父亲的十字架了吗？\NAnd did he give you back Daddy's crucifix?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:27.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如果你父亲能赶走一个一贫如洗的孩子\NIf your father's capable of throwing that boy out without a peny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:30.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他就不配把十字架挂在墙上\Nhe's got no right having Christ hanging all over his walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你们这些人根本就不知道什么是贫穷\NYou people don't understand what poverty is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.79,0:22:44.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你知道在查理维镇，如果他想看一本书\NDo you realise that in Charleville, if he wanted a book...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,还得去偷\Nhe had go and steal it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.79,0:22:50.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那恰恰证明了他的为人\NThat proves what kind of person he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.80,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:06.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你不该那样说他的\NYou shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:08.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:12.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 怎么了？  - 没什么\N- What's going on?   - Nothing.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:16.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,亲爱的，你没事吧？\NAre you all right, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:18.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我没事\NYes, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:44.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,去年夏天战时\NIt was last summer during the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:48.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我离家出走的一回\N one of the many times I ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:52.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我到河边装水\N I came down to the river to fill my water bottle...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.86,0:23:57.45,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有个没比我大多少的普鲁士兵\N and there was a Prussian soldier, not much older than me...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:23:59.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,在空地上睡觉\N asleep in the clearing.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:07.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我看了许久才明白\N I watched him for a long time before I realised...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.87,0:24:09.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他不是睡着\Nhe wasn't asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:11.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他是死了\Nhe was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这使我想通了\NAnd somehow that clarified things for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我若想成为本世纪第一诗人 \N I understood that what I needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.89,0:24:26.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我需要做的\Nto become the first poet of this century...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.89,0:24:30.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就是用我的身体力行一切\Nwas to experience everything in my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.90,0:24:36.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,作为一个人已不够\NIt was no longer enough for me to be one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.91,0:24:43.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我决定要成为每个人\N I decided to be everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.91,0:24:49.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,I decided to be a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.91,0:24:49.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,1,15,,我决定要成为一名天才式的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.63,0:24:55.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我决定要开创未来\N I decided to originate the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.94,0:25:19.37,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,谢谢\NThank you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.46,0:25:30.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,它的原理和摄影很相似\NThe principle is very like photography...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.96,0:25:33.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只不过不是拍下人的相貌\N only instead of photographing a man's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.96,0:25:35.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,而是记下他的声音\Nyou photograph his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.96,0:25:37.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,二十年后\N Then twenty years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.96,0:25:40.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就像打开相簿\Njust as you'd open a photograph album...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.31,0:25:44.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你只要将柱体放入机器\N you simply put the relevant cylinder into the paleophone...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.60,0:25:49.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就能听见诗人读他的诗\N and you listen to a poet reading his... reading his poems...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.36,0:25:51.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,或唱歌\N or singing his songs.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.69,0:25:54.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你认为你能发明\NAnd you think you... you could invent...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:57.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那么一种机器么?\N a machine like that which worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.57,0:25:59.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,天, 我们走吧\NFor Christ's sake, let's get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.62,0:26:01.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 不行    - 为什么？\N - We can't.   - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.79,0:26:04.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 他快要开始了   - 哪个？\N- He's about to start reading.   - Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.99,0:26:07.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,艾卡，那儿那个 \N Aicard.  Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.99,0:26:10.13,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不会喜欢他的\NOh, I don't think I'm going to like him very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.13,0:26:12.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,魏尔伦给我看过你的诗\N Verlaine showed me some of your poems.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.30,0:26:13.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,1,0,15,,Oh, Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.30,0:26:13.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,16,0,15,,噢，是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.76,0:26:16.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,了不起，很有前途\NRemarkable. Very promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.38,0:26:20.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只是，好像巧妙的构思被污染了..\NOnly it seems to me all that ingenuity is rather marred by...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.43,0:26:23.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,好像一个青年急切的想引起注意... \NWell, not exactly a juvenile urge to shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.26,0:26:24.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,类似这种意思\Nbut something of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.52,0:26:27.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 引起你注意了？   - 没\N- And were you shocked?  - No, I wasn't of course not.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.69,0:26:30.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那为什么你要假设我打算让你注意？\NThen why would you suppose I intended you to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.23,0:26:31.61,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,问题不在这里\NThat's not really the point.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.61,0:26:34.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我觉得理所当然\NSeems fair enough to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.02,0:26:36.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我反对你用的技巧\NI could object to your technical approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.02,0:26:37.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我反对你的领结\NI could object to your tie.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.07,0:26:41.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他不喜欢讨论他的诗\NHe doesn't like discussing his poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.03,0:26:43.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.03,0:26:43.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,1,15,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.03,0:26:47.29,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,给我们的朋友一个惊喜\NI have a surprise for our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.04,0:26:54.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.55,0:26:57.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,谢谢各位\NThanke you, thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.04,0:27:01.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,50,0,15,,- Sulfuric acid    - My first poem is written expressly for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.04,0:27:01.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,50,15,,- 硫酸       - 第一首是童诗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.05,0:27:03.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请各位记住\NI would ask you to bear this in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.05,0:27:05.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,所有有价值的儿童文学，\Nalthough, as with all worthwhile work for children...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.81,0:27:11.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,其实都不是完全和成年人无关的\Nit's hoped what is said is of some relevance to adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.06,0:27:12.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这首诗名为“绿色苦艾酒”\NThe poem is called "Green Absinthe."\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.27,0:27:16.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,绿色苦艾酒是受诅咒者的药\NGreen absinthe is the potion of the damned...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.78,0:27:20.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,阻塞血管的致命毒药\Na deadly poison silting up the veins...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.53,0:27:24.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,妻儿在贫贱中哭泣时\Nwhile wife and child sit weeping in their slum...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.07,0:27:27.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 我不信   - 醉汉将苦艾酒倾入脑中\N- I don't believe it.   - A drunkard pours absinthe into his brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.07,0:27:31.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,15,0,15,,- Shit.   - Oh drunkard, most contemptible of men...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.07,0:27:31.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 狗屁     - 酒鬼呀，最可厌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.08,0:27:33.59,微软雅黑0 1 30,,10,0,15,,- Shit!     - Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.08,0:27:33.59,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,20,15,,- 放屁       - 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.59,0:27:34.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,退化、堕落、罪恶、愚钝\NDegarded, fallen, sinful, and obtuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.84,0:27:38.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 完全狗屁不通！  - 别说了\N- It is! It's authentic shit!   - Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.08,0:27:41.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,退化、堕落、罪恶、愚钝\N...degraded, fallen, sinful, and obtuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.09,0:27:41.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我喜欢\NI like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.18,0:27:45.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你无所顾忌殴打妻儿\NYou scruple not to beat your wife and child...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.09,0:27:47.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为不给你酒喝\NFor trying to deprive you of the juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.27,0:27:49.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,50,15,,- Get out, you !   - Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.27,0:27:49.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,50,15,,- 你滚出去    - 我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:53.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对，就是你，你这个惹人厌的小杂种  快滚，不然就给你扔出去\NYes, you, you offensive little bastard. Get out, or I'll throw you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.10,0:27:55.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想应该允许我提出异议\NOh, I think I may, may I not, be permitted to raise some objection...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.77,0:27:57.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,法国诗被如此瞎搞\Nagainst the butchering of French poetry?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.86,0:28:00.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你没有这个权利，道完歉就滚\NNo, you may not. Now apologize and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.49,0:28:02.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别再靠近我\NDon't come any nearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.11,0:28:04.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,小心\NBe careful!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.11,0:28:07.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你以为你能吓着我\NYou think you can frighten me with that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.41,0:28:09.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,小心呀！\NCareful! Careful, I say!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.54,0:28:10.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.54,0:28:10.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.75,0:28:14.12,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,出去！\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.83,0:28:16.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,来呀 \NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.93,0:28:24.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你他妈的尿墨水的！现在到你了！\NNow you, you fucking inkpisser!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.30,0:28:25.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.30,0:28:25.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.72,0:28:27.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.72,0:28:27.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.14,0:28:32.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,在弗郎沙时代\NIn the days of Francois Premier...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.14,0:28:35.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,善良睿智的伟人们在乡间漫步\Nwise and benevolent giants roamed the countryside...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.14,0:28:37.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他们的主要职务之一\NAnd one of their primary functions...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.14,0:28:40.15,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就是清除世界上的学究\Nwas to rid the world of pedants...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.69,0:28:44.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,蠢材和和毫无才华的作家\Nfools and writers of no talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.15,0:28:49.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,而方法就是从高处往他们身上撒尿！\Nby pissing on them from a great height.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.60,0:29:13.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这就是怎么在文学界立足\NHow to make your way in the literary world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.19,0:29:21.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这个城市让人失望的就是…\NThe depressing thing about this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.19,0:29:25.36,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,搞艺术的比中产阶级还他妈的要中产阶级\Nis that the artists are even more bourgeois than the fucking bourgeoisie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.24,0:30:10.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们作个协定\NWe should make a bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.24,0:30:16.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你帮助我，我就帮助你\NYou help me, and I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.21,0:30:18.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如果你随我一起出走\NIf we go away together...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.33,0:30:21.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我保证你们一定能再创佳作\NI'm sure you'll be able to start doing good work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.25,0:30:25.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,各自取长补短之后\NAnd when we've taken as much as we can from each other...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.25,0:30:29.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们再分道扬镳\Nwe simply split up and move on.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.26,0:30:33.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们怎样度日？\NAnd how would we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.26,0:30:37.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你有钱的吧？\NYou have some money, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.27,0:30:43.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我懂了\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.27,0:30:45.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我资助你\NI help you by supporting you...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.27,0:30:49.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你帮我擦亮生命的灵感\Nand you help me by renewing my rusty old inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.28,0:30:51.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.28,0:30:51.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,是这意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.29,0:31:08.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,也不尽然\NNot altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.33,0:31:43.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.33,0:31:43.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,你去哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.00,0:31:47.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想我大概碍事了\NI thought I'd probably just get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.33,0:31:50.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Don't shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.33,0:31:50.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,别嚷！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.34,0:31:52.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,会吵到孩子\NYou'll wake the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.52,0:32:03.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Is it a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.52,0:32:03.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,是男孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.60,0:32:05.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.78,0:32:18.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,怪模怪样的小家伙\NFunny-looking little bugger.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.37,0:32:23.37,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不要\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.37,0:32:25.36,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.37,0:32:28.36,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,好吧\NAll right.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.40,0:32:51.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.40,0:32:57.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,真感谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.75,0:33:08.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.75,0:33:08.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.41,0:33:12.42,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,拜托，不要\NPlease...no
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.42,0:33:14.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Why not?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.42,0:33:14.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,为什么不？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.42,0:33:19.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,The baby was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.42,0:33:19.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,小孩都生下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.43,0:33:21.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不要\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.43,0:33:23.42,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不要\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.47,0:34:07.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,- Isabelle!    - I didn't know you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.47,0:34:07.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 伊莎贝拉！  - 我不知道你要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.47,0:34:09.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那个黑暗之嘴在哪？\NWhere is the mouth of darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:12.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,妈妈？她跟维达莉在田里\NMother? She's in the fields with Vitalie.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.90,0:34:14.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你想见她吗？\NDo you want to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.48,0:34:16.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,16,0,15,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.48,0:34:16.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不想
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.72,0:34:45.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.52,0:34:55.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Are you back for good?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.52,0:34:55.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,你回来就永远不走了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.52,0:34:57.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,永远我不知道\NFor good? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.52,0:34:59.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,For better or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.52,0:34:59.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.53,0:35:03.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,田里有事要做\NBecause there's work to be done in the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.16,0:35:05.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我这里也有事要做\NThere's work to be done here.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.16,0:35:08.12,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我以为你在巴黎混出名堂了\NI thought you were getting on well in Paris.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.37,0:35:11.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,本来就是，但最近魏尔伦的老婆开始找麻烦\N I was. But Verlaine's wife started to make trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.54,0:35:13.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么麻烦？\NWhat kind of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.54,0:35:15.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她扬言要离婚\NThreatening a divorce, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.67,0:35:18.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她认为我跟维尔伦呆在一起的时间太长\Nshe thought we were spending too much time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.54,0:35:21.55,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,娇生惯养的富家女，是吧？\NSpoiled rich girl, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.55,0:35:23.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没错\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.55,0:35:27.55,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你在做的事…\NThis work you're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.55,0:35:30.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有前途么？\Nis it the kind of thing that will lead to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.98,0:35:33.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.56,0:35:36.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但这是我要做的事\NNevertheless, it's the kind of work I do.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.62,0:36:40.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想巴黎没这么刺激吧\NI don't suppose Paris ever gets as exciting as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.71,0:38:07.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你看起来就像他妈的圣女\NYou look like a fucking saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.73,0:38:26.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就差个光环了\NExcept you haven't got your halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.74,0:38:37.73,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我来给你个光环\NI'll give you your halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.79,0:39:29.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他回来了，是吗？\NHe's back, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.39,0:39:37.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我现在不能离开她\NI can't leave Mathilde at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.60,0:39:38.80,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她身体不好\NShe's not very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.80,0:39:41.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,I'm not surprised if you keep setting fire to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:41.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,这到不奇怪，谁让你老是放火烧她。
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.81,0:39:45.80,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,星期四后我就没再烧过她\NI haven't set fire to her since Thursday.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.20,0:39:54.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,No, it's not very funny.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.20,0:39:54.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,15,0,15,,这不怎么好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.83,0:40:06.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不是可笑，是可悲\NNo, it's pathetic.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.83,0:40:10.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你的怪异暴行不是一般地让人恶心\NYour acts of violence are always curiously disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.84,0:40:12.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么意思？\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.84,0:40:16.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,一点都不干脆\NThey're not clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.84,0:40:20.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你老是醉得恍恍惚惚的\NYou're always in some sort of a drunken stupor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.85,0:40:23.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,事后就开始道歉乞怜\NThen you start apologizing and groveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.85,0:40:25.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不喜欢伤害人\NI don't like hurting people.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.61,0:40:27.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那就别做\NThen don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.53,0:40:30.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你要是做，就痛快点\NBut if you do, do it coolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.86,0:40:34.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别用道歉来侮辱受害者\NDon't insult your victims by feeling sorry afterwards.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.86,0:40:40.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我爱她，你是知道的\NI love her, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.46,0:40:43.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不可能\NYou can't possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.21,0:40:46.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我爱她的肉体\NI love her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.87,0:40:50.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,30,15,,- There are other bodies.    - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.87,0:40:50.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,30,15,,- 肉体有的是     - 不
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.34,0:40:52.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.88,0:40:55.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我爱玛蒂德的肉体\N I love Mathilde's body.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.88,0:40:58.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不爱她的灵魂？\NBut not her soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.26,0:41:03.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我认为爱肉体比爱灵魂更重要\NI think it's less important to love the soul than to love the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.02,0:41:04.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,毕竟灵魂可能是永存的\NAfter all, the soul may be immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.89,0:41:07.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们有的是时间去爱\NWe have plenty of time for the soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.19,0:41:10.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但肉体会腐烂\N but flesh rots.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.74,0:41:15.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,正是我对肉体的爱使我保持了忠诚\NIt's my love of flesh which keeps me faithful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.90,0:41:18.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Faithful？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.90,0:41:18.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,26,0,15,,忠诚？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.91,0:41:20.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么意思？\NWhat do you mean?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.79,0:41:24.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我忠于所有的爱人\NI'm faithful to all my lovers...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.91,0:41:26.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为只要我曾经爱过他们\Nbecause once I love them,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.91,0:41:30.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我就会永远爱他们\NI will always love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.92,0:41:32.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不管我是在夜间\NAnd when I'm alone in the evening...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.67,0:41:34.13,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,或是在茫茫清晨时独处\Nor in the early morning
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.13,0:41:35.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我会闭上眼睛\NI close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.84,0:41:38.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,赞颂他们每一个人\Nand I celebrate them all.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.39,0:41:44.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那不是忠贞，是怀旧\NThat's not faithfulness. That's nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.06,0:41:46.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你要是不想离开玛蒂尔德\NIf you don't want to leave Mathilde,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.69,0:41:50.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,也不是因为忠诚，而是因为你的软弱\Nit's not because you're faithful, it's because you're weak.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.52,0:41:53.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不，若强壮包括野蛮\N If strength involves brutality,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.07,0:41:55.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我宁愿选择软弱\NI prefer to be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.94,0:42:01.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你的话，软弱也同样带着野蛮，不是么？\NWith you, weakness involves brutality as well. Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.00,0:42:13.59,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别指望我忠于你\NDon't expect me to be faithful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.96,0:42:16.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你干嘛对我这么苛刻？\NWhy are you so harsh with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.43,0:42:18.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为你贱\NBecause you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:21.35,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你知道\NIsn't it enough for you to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.35,0:42:24.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我从没像爱你一样爱过别人\Nthat I love you more than I've ever loved anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.97,0:42:27.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,and that I'll always love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.97,0:42:27.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,我会永远爱你，难道还不够吗 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.27,0:42:30.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,闭嘴，你这醉鬼\NShut up, you sniveling drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.98,0:42:33.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 跟我说你爱我            - 哦, 天\N- Tell me that you love me.     -Oh, For God's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.61,0:42:35.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,求求你\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.65,0:42:39.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,求你了  这对我很重要\NPlease. It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.99,0:42:41.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.99,0:42:41.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,你说呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.99,0:42:50.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你知道我很喜欢你\NYou know I'm very fond of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.00,0:42:59.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,\N  - Do you love me?   - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.00,0:42:59.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(410,440)}- 你爱我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.00,0:42:59.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(539,440)}- 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.01,0:43:04.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- Do you love me?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.01,0:43:04.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(522,440)}- 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.01,0:43:04.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(420,440)}- 你爱我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.01,0:43:07.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那你就把手放桌上\NThen put your hands on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:10.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:10.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.65,0:43:13.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,把手放到桌上\NPut your hand on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.24,0:43:18.15,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,手心朝上\NPalm upwards.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.07,0:44:04.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,唯一不能忍受的，就是没什么是不能忍受的\NThe only unbearable thing is that nothing is unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.15,0:45:30.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,向前\NOn...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.16,0:45:34.15,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,向前\NOn...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.17,0:45:44.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们必须离开\NWe have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.17,0:45:47.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不知道\NI...I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.17,0:45:50.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,时候到了\NYes. It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.18,0:45:54.73,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,去年离家出走的时候是我一生中最快乐的时光\NThe happiest days of my life was last year when I ran away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.19,0:46:02.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有目的地，就那么继续往前走着\NI didn't know where I was going, I just carried on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.19,0:46:08.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我从没有过那么快乐的日子\NI've never seen such long and colored days...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.91,0:46:13.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只是我永远都走得不够远\Nand I could never get far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.20,0:46:14.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我还从没见过海\NI've never seen the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.20,0:46:17.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想去非洲\NI wanted to walk to Africa...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.20,0:46:20.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,穿越沙漠\Nand cross the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.59,0:46:22.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想要太阳\NI wanted the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.21,0:46:26.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想要太阳\NI wanted the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.21,0:46:29.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想要太阳\NI want the sun.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.21,0:46:32.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你明白吗？我要太阳！\NDo you understand me? I want the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.47,0:46:36.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你想去哪里？\NWhere do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.22,0:46:40.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.23,0:46:43.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不管，只要离开就行\NI don't care. Just away.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.23,0:46:45.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我现在不能离开玛蒂德\NYou know very well I can't leave Mathilde right now.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.49,0:46:46.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她身体不好\NShe's not very well.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.49,0:46:49.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那就不要\NThen don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.57,0:46:50.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.57,0:46:50.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(449,440)}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.78,0:46:54.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不要离开她\NDon't leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.80,0:48:35.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.80,0:48:35.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(444,440)}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.99,0:48:55.35,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,敬生命\NTo life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.42,0:50:01.42,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,来\NCome on!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.77,0:50:54.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,比利时，布鲁塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.58,0:52:33.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,保罗\NPaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.70,0:54:39.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你还记得那些快乐的时光么？\NDo you remember happier times?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.70,0:54:43.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你为何要离开我们？\NWhy did you leave us?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.71,0:54:48.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有风声说由于在巴黎公社期间  我在宣传部门工作过\NI had a tip-off I was going to arrested for my work...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.71,0:54:51.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,所以要遭到逮捕\Nin the propaganda press during the Commune.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.72,0:54:53.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但那是一年多以前的事了\NBut that was over a year ago.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.10,0:54:58.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,警方也许效率差\NWell... the police may be slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.35,0:55:00.73,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但总归还是行动派\Nbut they're methodical.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.73,0:55:02.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我可不能忍受进监狱\NI couldn't bear to go to jail.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.44,0:55:07.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,所以我觉得最好还是在国外呆几个月\NI think it's best if I stay out of the country for a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.36,0:55:10.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,与蓝波吗？\NWith Rimbaud?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.20,0:55:13.74,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,呃\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.74,0:55:16.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,想必警方也想抓他\NI suppose he's wanted by the police as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.12,0:55:19.73,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.75,0:55:24.63,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你为何宁可要他？\NWhy do you prefer him to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.75,0:55:26.74,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我没\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.88,0:55:28.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我没有\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.76,0:55:35.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你不用现在就穿上衣服吧？\NDon't have to get dressed right away, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.76,0:55:39.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我跟妈妈说了要一起吃早餐\NI told Mummy I'd meet her for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.76,0:55:42.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,\N- What's she doing here?  - She came with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.76,0:55:42.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(364,440)}- 她来干什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.76,0:55:42.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(540,440)}- 她陪我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.40,0:55:48.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对了，还有件事\NWell, that's another thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.11,0:55:52.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我再也受不了跟你的父母一起住了\NI certainly can't stand living with your parents anymore.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.99,0:55:55.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有别的安全的地方了\NIt's not safe anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.04,0:55:57.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么意思？\NWhat do you mean?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.78,0:55:59.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你明白我的意思\NYou know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.79,0:56:03.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,听我说\NListen...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.67,0:56:06.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我有个主意\NI had this idea.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.34,0:56:10.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是我想出来的\NI thought of this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.80,0:56:15.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想我们可以移民\NI thought we might emigrate.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.80,0:56:20.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,移民？去哪里？\NEmigrate? Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.69,0:56:21.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,新苏格兰\NNew Caledonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.52,0:56:26.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你有很多公社朋友在那边\NA lot of your friends from the Commune are there.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.44,0:56:29.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你可以写作\NYou'd be able to write.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.24,0:56:33.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就像我们刚结婚的时候，而且……\NIt would be like it was when we were first married and...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.82,0:56:36.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.82,0:56:36.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.82,0:56:38.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没什么\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.41,0:56:42.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不，说吧\NNo. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.21,0:56:48.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我只是想说，如果你愿意的话你可以不再……\NI was only going to say that you could stop...if you wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.71,0:56:54.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我是说，如果你心甘情愿的话  那戒酒会更容易些  \NI mean it would be easier for you if you wanted... to stop drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.85,0:57:07.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我把你吓坏了吧？\NYou're frightened of me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.85,0:57:13.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别以为我喜欢喝醉\NDon't think that I like getting drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.61,0:57:15.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我是说，我确实喜欢喝醉酒\NI mean, I do like getting drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.03,0:57:17.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但不喜欢就那么醉着\Nbut I don't like being drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.86,0:57:19.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不管怎样\NAnyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.87,0:57:22.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我打了你之后\Nwhen I hit you...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.87,0:57:25.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,感觉糟糕透了\NI feel so terrible all I can think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.46,0:57:28.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只能借酒消愁\Nis to get drunk again and forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.87,0:57:31.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你想我们能住在茅草屋里或是其他什么地方么？\NCan you see us living in a grass hut or whatever they have?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.88,0:57:33.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有何不可？\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.88,0:57:37.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Let's go, for Christ's sake, let's go. Before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.88,0:57:37.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,那就走吧，拜托，我们走吧。趁现在还来得及。
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.88,0:57:42.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只要你想，我们随时都可以离开\NWe can go whenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.40,0:57:53.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,现在不行\N Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.90,0:57:55.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.90,0:57:55.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,怎么不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.66,0:57:58.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,帮我扣上这个\NHelp me with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.54,0:58:01.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.91,0:58:03.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,帮我扣这个\NHelp me with this.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.91,0:58:05.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,住手\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.92,0:58:17.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你为何要这样对待我们？\NWhy are you doing this to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.34,0:58:20.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别担心\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.14,0:58:23.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他很快就会回到你身边\NYou can have him back quite soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.43,0:58:26.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只是有那么一点损伤\Nand only slightly damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.06,0:58:30.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他已经回来了\NHe's coming back now.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.20,0:58:46.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你来做什么？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.16,0:58:47.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.16,0:58:47.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.21,0:58:50.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,“我可怜的玛蒂德\N"My poor Mathilde...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.46,0:58:52.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别生气，别哭\N"Don't be upset. Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.67,0:58:53.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是噩梦\N"This is a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.96,0:58:56.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有天我会醒来的  爱你的保罗”\N"One day, I'll wake up. Love, Paul."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.96,0:59:00.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,甜蜜啊，是吧？闺房和乐？\NNice, was it? A scene of conjugal bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.51,0:59:02.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我要跟她回巴黎\NI'm going back to Paris with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.10,0:59:04.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,好啊\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.97,0:59:10.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- No, wait, wait, let me explain.  - Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.97,0:59:10.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(316.343,440)}- 别走，等一下，听我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.97,0:59:10.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(569.143,440)}- 我干嘛要听？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.98,0:59:13.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不是你想象的那样，是其他事\NIt's not what you think. It's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.69,0:59:15.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是她建议我们移民\NShe suggested we emigrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.23,0:59:16.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 移民？     -对 \N- Emigrate?  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.44,0:59:17.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,去新苏格兰\Nto New Caledonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.49,0:59:19.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,换个环境我就能过宁静的生活\NIt'd be a change for me. A quiet life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.07,0:59:20.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,还能戒酒   你不认为这是个好主意么？\NI could stop drinking, don't you think it's a good idea?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.99,0:59:22.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.66,0:59:25.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你根本就不在乎我是不是快乐，对吧?\NYou don't care about my happiness, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.50,0:59:26.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没错，你也不该在乎\NNo, and neither should you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.99,0:59:29.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你永远都不会明白我有多爱她\NYou've never been able to understand how much I love her.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.62,0:59:32.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,今天早上我走进来，她就躺在那，光着身子躺在床上。\N I walked in this morning, and she was lying there naked on the bed.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.00,0:59:35.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她看上去那么美，那么年轻，那么…\NShe looked so beautiful, so young and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.47,0:59:39.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有什么可笑的？\NWhat's so funny?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.00,0:59:40.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她真的光着身子躺在床上？\NWas she really lying there naked on the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.84,0:59:41.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对啊\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.01,0:59:44.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那我对她的评价可就要大幅度提高了\NThen my estimation for her goes up a long way.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.22,0:59:44.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么意思？为什么？\NWhat do you mean? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.89,0:59:48.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为她了解你想要什么并且迎合你的需要\NOh, for realizing what was needed and providing it for you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.23,0:59:52.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有什么关系？她是你老婆\NWhat does it matter? She's your wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.73,0:59:56.01,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你爱她，那就回她那儿去\Nyou love her, right? Go back to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.07,1:00:48.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,转车！转车！\NAll change! All change!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.74,1:00:50.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,边境巡逻！\NBorder patrol!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.54,1:00:54.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请拿好你们的护照以备检查\NPlease have your passports ready for inspection.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.08,1:00:57.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,边境巡逻！\NBorder patrol!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.08,1:01:01.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请拿好你们的护照以备检查\NPlease have your passports ready for inspection.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.12,1:01:35.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,谢谢\NThank you.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.51,1:01:49.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我去买份报纸\NI'm just going to find a newspaper.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.47,1:01:51.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别去太久\NDon't be long.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.78,1:02:06.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,玛蒂德\NMathilde
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.18,1:02:36.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,看\NLook there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.73,1:02:39.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- See white?   - Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.73,1:02:39.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(530,440)}- 对
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.73,1:02:39.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(400,440)}- 看见那白色吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.18,1:02:41.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.18,1:02:41.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,看到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.65,1:02:46.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那是英国\NIt's England.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.19,1:02:48.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,天啊！\NOh, oh, god!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.19,1:02:53.74,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(259.6,418.6)}伦敦，数月后
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.70,1:02:54.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(643.429,459.429)}我变成传说中的歌剧\N"I became a fabulous opera.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.16,1:02:55.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(442,470)}我变成传说中的歌剧\N"I became a fabulous opera.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.20,1:02:59.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,知晓一切生物都注定快乐\N"I saw that all creatures are condemned to happiness."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.21,1:03:05.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是什么？ 你重拾押韵了？\NWhat's this? Are you going back to rhyme?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.46,1:03:08.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,"我曾研究过究竟何为快乐\N"I have researched the magic shapes...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.34,1:03:11.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,它的魔力竟令人无法逃脱"\N"of the happiness no one escapes."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.22,1:03:15.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,真是绝妙\NThat's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.98,1:03:20.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我总是想不通为何你会选择把诗寄给我\NI've often wondered why you chose to write to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.86,1:03:24.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你远远地走在前面，我甚至看不懂你的那些符号\NYou are so far up ahead, I can't even understand the signs you're making.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.19,1:03:28.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你让我觉得我不属于这个世纪\NYou make me feel I'm from another century.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.99,1:03:34.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,“我曾研究过究竟何为快乐，它的魔力竟令人无法逃脱”\N"I have researched the magic shapes... of the happiness no one escapes."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.91,1:03:36.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,真妙\NIt's wonderful.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.50,1:03:40.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我会选择你当然是有原因的\NI chose you for a very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.83,1:03:43.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是这样的\NYou see...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.25,1:03:47.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我总是知道要说什么\NI've always known what to say...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.25,1:03:51.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,而你，你却知道如何去说\Nbut you... you know how to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.26,1:03:55.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想我能从你那学到点什么\NI thought I could learn from you...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.26,1:03:57.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,而且我确实学到了 \Nand I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.27,1:04:10.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你最怕什么？\NWhat's your greatest fear?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.41,1:04:15.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不想被阉\NI wouldn't like to mislay my balls. \N
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.58,1:04:17.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,怎么了？你最怕什么？\NWhy, what's your greatest fear?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.91,1:04:21.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,怕变成我眼中的别人\NThat other people will see me as I see them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.46,1:04:28.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们现在很缺钱\NGetting quite short of money, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.29,1:04:31.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你老说这个\NSo you keep saying.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.59,1:04:33.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,该找份工作\NPerhaps it's time we took a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.64,1:04:36.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我早就告诉过你了  我不打算找工作\NI've told you before, I've no intention of taking a job.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.60,1:04:38.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我的创作太好\NMy work is going far too well.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.22,1:04:42.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不能浪费时间赚钱\NI can't afford to waste time earning money.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.31,1:04:51.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我今早收到信\NI... I had a letter this morning...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.32,1:04:53.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,玛蒂德的律师来函\NFom Mathilde's lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.24,1:04:55.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,And?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.24,1:04:55.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.32,1:04:58.12,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她申请合法分居\NShe's applied for legal separation on the grounds...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.12,1:05:01.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为我俩有不道德关系\Nthat you and I are indulging in immoral relations.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.33,1:05:03.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,And?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.33,1:05:03.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,还有呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.33,1:05:06.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 喜欢这帽子，先生？     - 可能吧\N- Like a hat, sir?              - Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.33,1:05:08.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,来，看看\NThere you are. Take a look.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.67,1:05:15.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他想知道咱们是否愿作医学检查\NHe wants to know if we're prepared to submit to a medical examination.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.26,1:05:16.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.26,1:05:16.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.10,1:05:18.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,真不知道他们到底凭什么这么非难咱们\N I don't know why they think\N they can make that such outrageous accusation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.89,1:05:19.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,等会儿……\NWait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.72,1:05:20.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我要回信去骂他们这帮混蛋\N I'm going to write straight back,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.85,1:05:25.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,让他们对咱们的肛门尊敬点 \NI'm going to say as far as I'm concerned, the whole gang of them can look up our asses.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.02,1:05:26.61,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你疯了吗？\NWhat are you, insane?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.61,1:05:29.15,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她是被遗弃所以会获准离婚 \NThey can give her a divorce on desertion alone.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.15,1:05:32.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,而如果是遗弃外加鸡奸的话 我们就要坐牢了\Nand if it's desertion and sodomy, they can throw us both in jail.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.36,1:05:34.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我才不去坐牢\Nand I'm not going to jail.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.16,1:05:38.35,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是吗？有那么糟？\NI don't know. Would it be so bad?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.37,1:05:52.01,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,巴达维亚（雅加达）\NBatavia...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.17,1:05:56.37,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你能听到风吹过棕榈树叶的沙沙声\N You can hear the wind rustling in the palm trees.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.43,1:06:46.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不可能 (法语)\NL'IMPOSSIBLE.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.17,1:07:10.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,怎么了？\NWhat's the matter?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.46,1:07:15.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,太难了\NIt's so difficult.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.71,1:07:20.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,谁想到会这么难？\NWho would have imagined it would be so difficult?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.46,1:07:22.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我今天写信给律师了\NI wrote to the lawyer today.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.97,1:07:27.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,跟他解释说那是她父亲的错\NI explained to him, it's her father who's in the wrong.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.64,1:07:31.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我多次要求索回我的物品\NHow many times have I asked for my things back from that house?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.90,1:07:35.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,而她父亲都置之不理\NAnd he takes no...no notice whatsoever?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.78,1:07:38.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是你不对\NYou're in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.49,1:07:42.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,好吧\NAll right.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.49,1:07:45.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,好吧，是我不对\NAll right. I'm in the wrong.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.49,1:07:47.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是我错了，如果你想这么说的话\NI'm in the wrong, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.08,1:07:52.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你说是就是，对吧？\Nthen that's established, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.50,1:07:57.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.30,1:08:01.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What... What is it?  You seem different.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.30,1:08:01.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这到底是怎么了？  你像变了一个人似的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.51,1:08:04.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没错\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.51,1:08:07.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是写作的缘故\NIt's the writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.85,1:08:11.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,写作改变了我\NThe writing has changed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.53,1:08:28.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,前进\NOn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.53,1:08:30.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,前进\NOn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.54,1:08:33.38,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,前进\NOn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.46,1:08:36.55,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,前进\NOn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.42,1:08:38.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,前进\NOn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.34,1:08:40.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,前进\NOn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.22,1:08:48.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,前进\NOn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.56,1:08:50.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,前进\NOn.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.59,1:09:29.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你大概认为这几周来\NI suppose you think I've been just lying here...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.06,1:09:32.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我一直都像瘫了似的躺在床上吧？\Nall these weeks in a state of paralyzed sloth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.60,1:09:35.59,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,呃，倒也不是\NWell, not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.60,1:09:39.59,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我确实是\NWell, I have.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.61,1:09:43.61,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但在漠然的外表下翻搅着\NBut bubbling beneath the surface...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.61,1:09:47.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,并且缓缓浮现的，是崭新的体制\Nand rising slowly through the layers of indifference has come a new system...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.24,1:09:49.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,树立坚韧无情\Nharden up
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.91,1:09:51.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,扬弃浪漫主义\Nreject romanticism...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.83,1:09:53.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,抛开辞藻\Nabandon rhetoric...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.37,1:09:57.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,直击要害\NGet it right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.21,1:10:02.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我终于见到了想征服世界的下场\NAnd finally I've seen where my attempt to conquer the world has led me.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.63,1:10:04.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么下场？\NWhere has it led you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.64,1:10:12.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,流落至此\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.85,1:10:19.63,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,想要体验一切却落到这步田地\NMy search for universal experience has led me here...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.02,1:10:25.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,活在闲散、无意义的穷困中\Nto live an idle, pointless life of poverty...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.65,1:10:32.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,被一个老诗人宠幸\Nas the minion of a bald, ugly...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.70,1:10:35.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他又秃又丑，酒气昏天的\Naging, drunken lyric poet...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.66,1:10:40.38,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他死缠着我   因为他老婆不让他回去\Nwho clings to me because his wife won't take him back.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.67,1:10:44.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你怎能说这种话？\NHow can you bring yourself to say a thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.59,1:10:46.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,很简单\NIt's easy. \N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.67,1:10:48.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是事实\NIt's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.30,1:10:51.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你就在这，就这么活着，因为你不得不如此\NYou're here living like this because you have to...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.97,1:10:55.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,酗酒、做爱、自以为是的忧郁\Ndrink and sex and a kind of complacent melancholy...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.93,1:10:58.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有钱就去夜夜买醉好忘记一切\Nand enough money to soak yourself oblivious every night.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.98,1:11:02.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,可我不同，我在这是因为我选择了这种生活\NBut me... l'm here because I choose to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.48,1:11:04.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Oh, yes?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.48,1:11:04.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,噢，是么？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.65,1:11:06.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,当然\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.91,1:11:14.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,And why exactly?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.91,1:11:14.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,那到底是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.16,1:11:19.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,为什么当初选择跟我到伦敦来？\NWhy did you choose to come to London with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.92,1:11:24.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,显然你把这当成了你的秘密流浪的一个舞台\NNo doubt you regarded it as another stage in your private odyssey...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.71,1:11:28.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只有越陷越深\Nonly by plunging ever deeper, if I may mix my myths...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.71,1:11:32.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你才有资格在诗坛往上爬\Nwill you gain the right to graze on the slopes of Parnassus.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.72,1:11:40.35,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,当然，还有简单得多的理由让你一直忍受着我\NOf course there are less subtle reasons for putting up with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.15,1:11:42.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Such as?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.15,1:11:42.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,23,0,15,,例如呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.98,1:11:45.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,例如我养着你这个事实\NSuch as the fact that I support you.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.74,1:11:55.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你的心几乎跟身体一样丑\NYour mind is almost as ugly as your body.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.75,1:12:11.80,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你要去哪？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.11,1:12:27.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- Are they fresh?   - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.11,1:12:27.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(366,440)}- 新鲜吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.11,1:12:27.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(545,440)}- 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.78,1:12:35.12,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这一只\NThis one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.09,1:12:54.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,老天，看你那一脸贱相。\NGod, you look such a cunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.61,1:13:07.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你去哪里？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.48,1:13:11.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你去哪里？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.82,1:13:15.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别走\NWait!\N
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.82,1:13:17.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,等一下，保罗\NPaul, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.91,1:13:19.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,保罗\N Paul.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.83,1:13:28.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.83,1:13:28.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,让开！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.46,1:13:34.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Paul, don't go!\N
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.46,1:13:34.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,保罗，别走！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.84,1:13:36.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.84,1:13:36.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,27,0,15,,回来啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.14,1:13:37.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别丢下我\NDon't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.84,1:13:41.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.84,1:13:41.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,快回来呀！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.85,1:13:44.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对不起\NI'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.98,1:13:51.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.98,1:13:51.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,真的对不起！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.86,1:13:56.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我怎么活下去啊？\NHow am I supposed to live?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.32,1:13:58.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,回来\NCome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.86,1:14:02.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,求你快回来，你是我唯一的朋友\NPlease come back. You're my only friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.87,1:14:05.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我答应你我会乖乖的\NI promise you I'll behave myself.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.62,1:14:07.38,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那只是个愚蠢的玩笑罢了\NIt was only a stupid joke.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.50,1:14:07.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,先生？\NSir?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.96,1:14:10.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我真的好抱歉\NI can't tell you how sorry I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.13,1:14:16.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,500,0,15,,{\pos(279,390)}布鲁塞尔，数日后
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.17,1:14:14.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,When I called you, why didn't you get off the boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.17,1:14:12.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我叫你时为何不下船？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.92,1:14:14.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(600,440)}我叫你时为何不下船？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.88,1:14:19.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们一起生活了两年，难道非得这样结束么？\NWe lived together for two years to finish like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.89,1:14:24.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,回想一下你在遇到我之前的样子\NThink back to what you were before you met me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.89,1:14:27.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,听从你的心\NListen to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.52,1:14:31.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你永远的蓝波\NYours for always.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.93,1:15:11.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,明天我就回巴黎\NI'll go back to Paris tomorrow.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.82,1:15:17.40,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别\N No,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.94,1:15:20.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,听我说\Nlook,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.95,1:15:24.58,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不会再发生这样的事了\Nit won't happen again,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.95,1:15:28.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我绝不会再丢下你一个人，我保证\NI'll never walk out on you again, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.21,1:15:30.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对，你不会了\NNo, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.95,1:15:33.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不会再让你有这个机会了\NI'm not going to give you the chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.55,1:15:38.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 我身无分文地呆在伦敦能干什么？   - 对不起 \NWhat was I supposed to do in London with no money?    - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.22,1:15:40.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我当时很生气\NI was very hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.96,1:15:43.64,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是为什么啊？\NFor God's sakes, why?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.01,1:15:47.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我以前说过比那过分得多的话\NI've said far worse things to you than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.98,1:16:01.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,而且你的确是一脸贱相\NYou really did look like a cunt.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.70,1:16:43.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你去哪儿了？\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.03,1:16:50.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,外面\NOut.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.21,1:16:52.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我又去了西班牙大使馆\NI went to the Spanish embassy again...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.46,1:16:54.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,看看他们会不会改变主意    但他们没有\Nto see if they'd change their minds, but they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.71,1:16:57.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,荒谬, 真他妈的荒谬\NIt's ridiculous. It's fucking ridiculous.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.04,1:17:00.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我说愿为他们战死\N"I'm willing to fight", I said, "and die for your cause."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.84,1:17:02.55,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你们怎么能拒绝志愿者\N"You can't afford to turn away volunteers."\N
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.55,1:17:05.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但他们却说不要外国人\NBut they said they weren't taking on any foreigners.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.05,1:17:07.31,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,然后我就咒他们活该战败\NThen I said, "You deserve to lose the fucking war...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.31,1:17:08.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我希望你们战败\N"and I hope you do."\N
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.10,1:17:11.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你整个早上都在西班牙大使馆吗？\NAnd were you at the Spanish Embassy all morning?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.06,1:17:13.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.06,1:17:16.36,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你喝醉了\NYou're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.61,1:17:21.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我是喝了几杯\NI have, yes, had a few drinks.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.07,1:17:24.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你在干什么？\NWhat are you doing?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.07,1:17:26.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,收拾行李\NPacking.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.07,1:17:27.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你要上哪去？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.83,1:17:29.74,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,回洛许老家\NI'm going back home to Roche.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.07,1:17:33.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,把书写完，将它出版\NI'm going to finish my book and I'm going to have it published.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.08,1:17:35.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,噢，出版？\NOh, publish.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.08,1:17:39.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我以为你没把出版放在眼里呢\NI thought you were far too important for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.08,1:17:41.59,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不管怎样，听着，我决定了，我们得回伦敦。\NAnyway, listen, I've decided. We're going back to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.09,1:17:43.38,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不会跟你回伦敦的\NWe're not going back to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.43,1:17:46.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你会的，我已经仔细考虑过了，这是目前为止最好的办法。\NYes, Yes, Yes. I've been thinking, it's by far the best idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.76,1:17:48.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那你干嘛去西班牙大使馆？\NThen why did you go to the Spanish embassy?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.85,1:17:49.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我没去\NI didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.52,1:17:55.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别走，再考虑考虑\NDon't go. Think it over.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.10,1:17:57.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我已经考虑过了\NI've thought it over.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.11,1:18:09.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你知道明天是什么日子么？\NDo you know what day it is tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.11,1:18:11.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,星期五\NFriday.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.45,1:18:14.29,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是我的结婚纪念日\NIt's my wedding anniversary...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.46,1:18:16.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,从上次在布鲁塞尔做爱后\Nand I haven't seen her, my wife...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.75,1:18:20.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我有一年没见过我妻子\Nsince we made love here in Brussels nearly a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.05,1:18:21.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,她不回我的信\NShe won't answer my letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.80,1:18:26.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,知道么，上周我写信告诉她，三天内她不来布鲁塞尔\NDo you know, I wrote her last week and told her if she didn't come to Brussels within 3 days...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.47,1:18:29.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我就自杀  她甚至连信都没回\N I'd commit suicide. And she didn't even reply.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.26,1:18:32.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,啊，但你也没自杀啊\NAh, but then you didn't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.68,1:18:35.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你大概觉得很可笑\NI suppose you think that's funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.14,1:18:37.35,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不，是很可怜\NNo, it's pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.60,1:18:42.15,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你到底跟多少人说过要自杀？\NTell me. How many people did you write and tell you were going to committ suicide?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.15,1:18:46.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我真吃惊你居然没发请贴\NI'm surprised you didn't send out invitations.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.53,1:18:51.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你怎么能这么冷酷无情？\NHow can you be so callous?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.91,1:18:56.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,无情？我冷酷无情？！你把我丢在伦敦\NCallous?  Callous?!  You abandon me in London...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.50,1:18:58.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,又要我来布鲁塞尔陪你\Nand then summon me to Brussels and expect me to hang around...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.83,1:19:01.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,而你却在决定到底是要离开你老婆\N while you decide whether you're going to leave your wife...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.16,1:19:03.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,参军，还是自杀？\Njoin the army, or shoot yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.17,1:19:05.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,然后当你发现你显然一样都干不了的时候\NThen when you fail to achieve any of these aims...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.72,1:19:09.17,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,还要我陪你回伦敦\Nas you undoubtedly will, you want me to go back to London with you!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.17,1:19:11.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我才不去！  休想    我要离开你 ！\NIt's not gonna happen! Forget it. I'm leaving you!\N
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.64,1:19:12.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你不能这样\NYou can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.72,1:19:15.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你不能！\NYou can't!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.44,1:19:18.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,听我说\NLook,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.18,1:19:20.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,现在正是夏天\Nit's summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.18,1:19:22.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,难道你不记得去年夏天我们一起出去旅行的日子...\NRemember last summer when we set out...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.77,1:19:25.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有多么快乐?\Nhow wonderful it was?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.19,1:19:27.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你记得吗？\NRemember?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.19,1:19:30.78,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们这次何不去南方看看？\NWhy don't we go south?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.95,1:19:33.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,去年夏天在地中海\NLate summer on the Mediterranean...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.20,1:19:35.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们享受着热情\Nwe could dedicate ourselves to warmth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.20,1:19:36.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,或去非洲\NOr Africa.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.71,1:19:38.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我知道你一直想去非洲\NI know you've always wanted to go to Africa.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.79,1:19:41.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,只去一个月，快决定吧\NJust for a month, then make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.04,1:19:43.59,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,去看太阳\NLook at the sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.21,1:19:46.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不要\NNo.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.21,1:19:50.20,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,为什么？\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.22,1:19:54.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不能去\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.22,1:19:57.18,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没用的\NIt's no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.60,1:20:03.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- It's too late.   - It's not!  It's not!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.60,1:20:03.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(346,440)}- 太晚了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.60,1:20:03.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(532,440)}- 不晚！一点都不晚！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.73,1:20:07.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我保证还不晚\NI promise you, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.16,1:20:12.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你若抛弃我就是杀了我\NYou know if you leave me, you'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.32,1:20:16.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我无法……我无法忍受孤单\NI can't... I can't bear to be alone.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.62,1:20:19.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有别人我活不了\NI don't exist without someone else.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.29,1:20:24.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不管你是不是出于同情，只要留下来就行\NI don't care if you stay with me out of pity, just stay!\N
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.46,1:20:31.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- I can't.    - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.46,1:20:31.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(366,440)}- 我不能
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.46,1:20:31.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(524,440)}- 为什么不能？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.34,1:20:33.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你不在乎\NYou don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.26,1:20:34.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你一点都不关心我  难道你不知道这对我意味着什么么？\NYou have no idea what this means to me.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.93,1:20:37.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,妈的，你别嚎了\NFor God's sake, stop whining!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.26,1:20:43.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,好热\NIt's very hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.27,1:20:46.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,脱掉外套\NTake off your coat.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.27,1:20:50.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我会的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.27,1:20:55.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,早上我买了点东西\NI did some shopping this morning.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.28,1:21:00.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我买了把枪\NI bought a gun.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.28,1:21:02.29,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.28,1:21:02.29,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.29,1:21:06.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,为你，为我，为每个人\NFor you, for me, for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.30,1:21:16.29,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,希望你买了很多子弹\NI hope you bought plenty of ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.31,1:21:28.31,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不会让你走的\NI'm not going to let you go, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.31,1:21:31.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这倒是个新鲜的花招，\NThis is a rather entertaining number.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.53,1:21:32.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们还从没用过这个\NWe haven't seen this one before.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.86,1:21:34.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我要杀了你！\NI'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.32,1:21:36.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,天，你控制一点\NFor God's sake, pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.70,1:21:38.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我看了你的信\NI read your letter.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.83,1:21:41.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你求我回来的\NYou begged me to come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.45,1:21:43.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你说你边写边哭\NYou said you were crying as you wrote it.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.79,1:21:46.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我能看到那纸上的泪痕！\NI could see your tears on the paper!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.96,1:21:53.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那时我还没想到典当你的衣物\NThat was before I thought of pawning your clothes.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.78,1:22:17.82,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不是故意的\NI didn't mean to.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.36,1:22:20.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,瞧你干的好事\NLook what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.36,1:22:24.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,抱歉，我不是有意的\NI didn't mean to. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.54,1:22:25.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.37,1:22:30.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,噢，天，杀了我吧，开枪啊\NOh, for God's sake, kill me, shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.38,1:22:35.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.38,1:22:35.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,23,0,15,,开枪呀！
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.38,1:22:36.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我怎么开枪？你这个蠢货\NHow can I, you stupid fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.76,1:22:38.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你在我手上开了个洞\NYou've just blown a hole in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.39,1:22:41.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Oh, God. What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.39,1:22:41.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,噢，上帝，我都干了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.44,1:22:48.61,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- 你没命中   - 开门\N- You missed.   -Open up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.39,1:22:51.38,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.39,1:22:51.38,微软雅黑0 1 30,,28,0,15,,开门！
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.40,1:22:55.39,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,开门啊！\NOpen up in there!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.40,1:22:59.40,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你到底在布鲁塞尔干什么？\NWhat exactly are you doing in Brussels?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.40,1:23:02.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我期待妻子来这儿与我会合\NI was hoping my wife might come and join me here...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.41,1:23:05.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就像分居后她也曾经做过的那样\Nas she had already done on one occasion since our separation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.87,1:23:08.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不明白，一个朋友的离去\NI fail to see how the departure of a friend...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.25,1:23:10.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,竟会使你如此绝望\Ncould have cast you into such despair.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.54,1:23:13.42,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你与兰波之间是否有……\NDid there perhaps exist between you and Rimbaud...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.42,1:23:15.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,超出友谊的关系？\Nother relations besides those of friendship?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.42,1:23:17.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.42,1:23:22.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是我妻子和她娘家\NThis is a suggestion slanderously invented...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.72,1:23:26.42,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,对我的诽谤\Nby my wife and her family.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.96,1:23:54.13,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,脱下裤子，趴在桌上\NTake off your trousers and lie on this, face down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.47,1:24:06.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,两位医生都已作证\NBoth doctors have testified...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.47,1:24:08.31,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,根据检验\Nthat on the basis of their examination...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.47,1:24:13.19,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他们肯定你在最近一段时间内曾有过鸡奸行为\Nthey are satisfied that you have recently indulged in both active and passive sodomy.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.19,1:24:14.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Have they?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.19,1:24:14.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,20,0,15,,他们说的？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.48,1:24:17.11,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你否认鸡奸行为？\NDo you deny you're a practicing sodomist?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.11,1:24:19.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,正确说法应该是肛交\NThe word is sodomite.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.48,1:24:22.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不管它被称为什么\NWhatever the word may be, the activity it describes...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.95,1:24:25.62,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,布鲁塞尔不赞成这种行为\Nis not one which is encouraged in Brussels.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.59,1:24:38.42,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,保罗.魏尔伦，本庭判你有罪\NPaul-Marie Verlaine, the court finds you guilty...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.50,1:24:41.50,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,依据刑法三九九条\Nunder Article 399 of the penal code...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.50,1:24:44.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,严重伤害罪，判处你……\Nof grievous bodily harm and sentences you...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.05,1:24:49.48,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,罚金两百法郎，并监禁两年\Nto a fine of two hundred francs and two years' imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.55,1:25:31.55,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,又怎么了？\NNow what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.55,1:25:33.55,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,魏尔伦 \NVerlaine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.56,1:25:38.55,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Verlaine！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.56,1:25:38.55,微软雅黑0 1 30,,28,0,15,,魏尔伦！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.56,1:25:43.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,吃饭\NEat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.76,1:28:59.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,上帝\NGod.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.31,1:29:42.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.31,1:29:42.77,微软雅黑0 1 30,,27,0,15,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.81,1:29:46.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我看不懂它想要说什么\NI don't understand what it's supposed to mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.81,1:29:49.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我写了什么就是什么意思\NIt means exactly what it says...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.81,1:29:51.61,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,每个字都有它的用处\Nword for word,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.81,1:29:54.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,一字不多，一字不少\Nno more, no less.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.84,1:30:25.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(676,434.533)}黑森林，两年后
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.85,1:30:33.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你好吗？\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.24,1:30:36.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你的念珠呢？\NWhere's your rosary?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.37,1:30:39.66,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我以为你戴念珠\NI thought you'd have a rosary.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.33,1:30:43.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你在牢里真被称作耶稣？\NIs it true in prison they called you Jesus Christ?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.87,1:30:48.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,起因很突然\NIt happened quite suddenly.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.58,1:30:51.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那天我得知玛蒂德获准离婚\Nthe day the governor told me Mathilde had been granted her divorce.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.87,1:30:55.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我躺下，回首一生\NI lay down and looked at my life...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.22,1:30:58.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么都看不到，一无所有\Nand saw there was nothing, nothing.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.76,1:31:02.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,似乎我唯一能做的事就是把自己交给主\NIt seemed to me the only thing I could do was to submit myself to God...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.89,1:31:04.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请求他的宽恕\Nask him to forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.23,1:31:07.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,并帮助我面对当时的处境    而且主真的帮了我\Nand help me face my situation and He did.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.89,1:31:10.89,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我保证他会的\NI promise you, He did.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.89,1:31:13.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,现在你想让我们在主的庇佑下相亲相爱，对吧？\NNow you want us to love each other in Jesus, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.19,1:31:16.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我希望你以我为榜样\NI want you to follow my example.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.78,1:31:21.37,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但愿你没以为我一直在生你的气\NI hope you didn't think, all this time, I might be angry with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.37,1:31:22.16,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我没有 \NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.54,1:31:25.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我知道你也没想到我会被关这么久\NI know you had no idea I might be put away for so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.54,1:31:27.29,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我早就原谅你了\NI certainly forgave you for it.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.42,1:31:31.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- I didn't forgive you.   - What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.42,1:31:31.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(372.667,440)}- 我没原谅你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.42,1:31:31.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(528.667,440)}- 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.91,1:31:33.46,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你没命中\NFor missing.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.96,1:31:37.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你为何来这里？\NTell me. Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.92,1:31:42.91,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我希望你找到人生的方向\NI want you to find some direction in your life.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.93,1:31:46.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我希望主能帮你实现你的目标\NI want God to help you achieve your aims.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.93,1:31:49.93,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,目标？我没有目标\NAims? I have no aims.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.93,1:31:52.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- I mean your writing.    - I've stopped writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.93,1:31:52.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(346.334,440)}- 我是指你的写作
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.93,1:31:52.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(525,440)}- 我封笔了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.94,1:31:54.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不懂……\NI don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.94,1:31:56.44,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那就换个说法\NLet me put it another way.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.61,1:31:58.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不再写作了\NI no longer write.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.36,1:32:00.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,为什么？\NWhy not?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.94,1:32:02.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为我已经没什么好说的了\NBecause I have nothing more to say.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.95,1:32:05.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,其实一开始就没什么可说的\NIf I ever had anything to say in the first place.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.95,1:32:07.94,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,胡扯\NNonsense.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.95,1:32:12.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我曾以为我能做些什么，你知道\NI thought that what I did would make a difference, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.96,1:32:14.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,改变世界\Nchange the world.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.96,1:32:18.42,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想一切都将不同\NI thought nothing would ever be the same again.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.96,1:32:21.96,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但都没用\NBut it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.96,1:32:25.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,世界太老，没新鲜事\NThe world is too old, there's nothing new,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.97,1:32:27.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,话都已经被别人说过了\Nit's all been said.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.97,1:32:31.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但由你来说就不同.你有天赋\NNot in the way you can say it. You have a gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.23,1:32:35.27,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别为不实际的期望而放弃\NIt's no good throwing it away because your expectations were unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.27,1:32:38.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你应该改变的是期望\NIt's the expectations you should change.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.98,1:32:42.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,天赋是我的，我想怎样就怎样\NIt's my gift, I can do what I like with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.99,1:32:45.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你不能放弃，你甚至还没开始呢\NYou can't give up, you've hardly begun.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.99,1:32:48.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别担心  我会很好的\NDon't worry. I'll be very good at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.99,1:32:51.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没人能动得了我：\NNo one will be able to touch me:
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.99,1:32:53.99,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,沉默的天才\NThe master of silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.46,1:32:59.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,如果我们不说，谁来阐述真理？\NBut if we don't, who's going to tell the truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.00,1:33:02.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,三年前，你说真理是这个，真理是那个\NThree years ago, you said the truth was this and the truth was that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.00,1:33:04.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,然后天使降临\NThen along comes the angel of the Lord...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.22,1:33:08.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你的真实随即改观\Nand the next day the truth is something completely different.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.27,1:33:11.01,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但我已经改变了，变了\NBut I've changed, change...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.01,1:33:14.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我想这正是你想要的\NI thought that was what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.02,1:33:16.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,变了，你么？\NYou've changed, have you?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.02,1:33:18.01,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.02,1:33:18.01,微软雅黑0 1 30,,26,0,15,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.95,1:33:27.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那就在这，在这片荒野中\NThen here, in the wilderness...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.03,1:33:30.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我让你做个选择：\NI offer you an archetypal choice:\N
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.66,1:33:32.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是要我的身体，\Na choice between my body,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.04,1:33:36.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,还是我的灵魂\Nand my soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.04,1:33:39.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,选吧\NChoose.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.04,1:33:42.03,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,选啊\NChoose.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.64,1:33:48.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你的身体\NYour body.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.05,1:33:53.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,看，你的主的九十八道伤口爆裂，鲜血直流\NLet the ninety-eight wounds of Our Savior burst and bleed.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.06,1:34:01.05,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,别\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.07,1:34:10.45,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,听我说，我曾坐在牢房里\NListen... I sat in my cell...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.45,1:34:13.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,想着我们能有多快乐\Nand thought how happy we could be.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.08,1:34:16.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这应该很容易的，这该是世上最容易的事\NIt should be, should be the easiest thing in the world.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.54,1:34:17.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,为何没能实现呢？\NWhy isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.71,1:34:21.08,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为我们根本办不到\NBecause it never worked for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.08,1:34:24.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们俩谁也办不到\Nand it will never work for either of us.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.09,1:34:28.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我曾想咱们两个人能一起离开\NI wanted us to go away together.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.09,1:34:30.09,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,嗯\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.47,1:34:32.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我该做些什么？\NWhat am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.93,1:34:36.31,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你得另找别人\NYou'll have to find somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.31,1:34:39.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我做不到，求你了\NNo, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, I can't, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.52,1:34:40.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,放手\NLet go.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.10,1:34:41.10,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,求求你\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.10,1:34:44.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Let go! Let go!\N
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.10,1:34:44.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,27,0,15,,放开！放手！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.08,1:36:22.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我会带着钢铁般的四肢归来\N"I shall return with limbs of steel...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.21,1:36:27.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,还有黝黑的皮肤和愤怒的双眼\N"a dark skin and a wrathful eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.21,1:36:29.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我将富有：\N"I shall have money:
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.80,1:36:33.72,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,变得残酷无情，无所事事\N"I shall be cruel and idle.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.60,1:36:36.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我将得到救赎\N"I'll be saved."
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.22,1:36:40.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.22,1:36:40.22,微软雅黑0 1 30,,30,0,15,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.22,1:36:42.21,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他的诗\NSomething he wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.73,1:36:45.40,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我的意思是，维尔伦先生，坦白地说\NThe point is, Mr. Verlaine, to speak frankly...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.40,1:36:48.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他年轻时候写了很多诗作\Na number of the poems he wrote in extreme youth...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.23,1:36:49.90,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是非常淫秽\Nwere quite indecent...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.82,1:36:53.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,甚至亵渎神灵的\Nand in some cases, even profane.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.37,1:36:56.24,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他绝不想因为这些而被世人记住\NHe would never have wished to be remembered for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.54,1:36:59.71,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,是的，家母和我计划去芜存菁\NMy mother and I plan to destroy those of his works
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.71,1:37:01.92,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,销毁那些不好的作品\Nwe feel he would have destroyed himself\N
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.92,1:37:03.04,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我明白了\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.25,1:37:09.25,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,或许你还不知道\NWhat you may not know...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.25,1:37:13.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,亚瑟皈依天主教了\Nis that Arthur was converted.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.26,1:37:15.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,皈依了？\NConverted?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.26,1:37:16.47,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我对他讲道理\NI reasoned with him...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.26,1:37:21.06,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他病时我为他祈祷数周\Nand prayed for him for weeks while he was ill...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.27,1:37:27.26,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,最终他要求忏悔\Nand eventually he asked to be confessed.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.27,1:37:31.70,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,上帝给了他足够的时间忏悔\NGod kept him alive long enough to repent...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.27,1:37:34.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他会得到救赎的\Nso that he could be saved.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.37,1:37:36.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他出了什么事？\NWhat was the matter with him?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.28,1:37:38.37,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他的膝盖长了肿瘤\NHe had a tumor on his knee.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.71,1:37:43.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,真是怪事\NThat's very strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.75,1:37:45.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,Why?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.75,1:37:45.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.50,1:37:52.28,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,因为我正好也有这毛病：膝盖上长了肿瘤\NThat's what I have: a tumor on my knee.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.30,1:37:56.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他在阿比西尼亚待了十年\NHe spent ten years in Abyssinia.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.30,1:37:58.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他的足迹遍布整个国家\NHe explored the whole country...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.30,1:38:01.30,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,深入白人从未去过的地方\Nplaces no white man had ever been...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.30,1:38:04.31,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他在哈勒尔经营贸易站\Nand he ran a trading post in Harar.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.19,1:38:07.23,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那地方没有医生\NThere was no doctor there...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.31,1:38:10.31,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,但他不愿放下工作\Nbut he wouldn't leave his work.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.31,1:38:14.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他坚持到疼得再也无法忍受\NHe insisted on staying until the pain became unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.28,1:38:17.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,然后自己设计一具担架\NThen he designed himself a litter...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.32,1:38:21.31,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,雇了十人抬到海边\Nand hired ten men to carry him to the coast.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.32,1:38:26.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,航程超过两星期\NThe journey took more than two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.33,1:38:29.32,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,在非洲时…\NIn Africa...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.21,1:38:34.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他会写诗吗？\NDid he write poetry?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.34,1:38:36.33,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.80,1:39:55.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,On!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.80,1:39:55.34,微软雅黑0 1 30,,27,0,15,,向前！
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.01,1:39:56.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,On!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.01,1:39:56.97,微软雅黑0 1 30,,27,0,15,,向前！
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.68,1:40:09.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,一抵达法国\NFirst, as soon as he arrived...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.81,1:40:13.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他就进了马塞的医院\Nhe went into the hospital in Marseilles...\N
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.44,1:40:17.43,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他们锯掉了他的腿\Nand they cut off his leg.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.49,1:41:11.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,怎么了？\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.04,1:41:15.49,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你看见那些从天而降的马车了么？\NCan you see the carriages driving in the sky?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.51,1:41:28.51,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我必须要帮助别人，你知道\NI have to help people, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.51,1:41:30.02,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这是我的责任\NIt's my duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.51,1:41:32.52,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我知道\NI know you do.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.52,1:41:36.61,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我不想要钱，除非它们浸透了鲜血\NI don't want money, unless it's drenched in blood.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.61,1:41:38.61,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,嗯\NSsh.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.53,1:41:46.37,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,或许海水能冲洗掉污痕\NMaybe the sea will wash away the stains.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.62,1:41:50.41,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,也许\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.13,1:41:59.00,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,有件事，伊莎贝拉，你一定要答应我\NThere's one thing, Isabelle, you must promise me,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.00,1:42:01.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,这很重要，你能答应我么？\Nit's very important, will you promise?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.54,1:42:03.53,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,什么事？\NWhat?\N
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.55,1:42:11.54,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,绝不要让他们截肢\NNever let them amputate.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.57,1:42:26.45,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他只肯在家停留一个月\NHe would only stay at home a month.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.57,1:42:32.56,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他一直说，他得返回太阳下\NHe kept saying he had to travel back towards the sun,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.58,1:42:37.57,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,太阳能治愈他\Nthat the sun would heal him.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.65,1:43:49.74,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,请别站起来了\NPlease, don't get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.91,1:43:52.95,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我送你回旅馆\NLet me see you to your hotel.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.95,1:43:55.45,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,不用了，很荣幸……\NNo, no. It was an honor...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.45,1:43:57.79,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,见到您这样一位杰出的诗人\Nto meet such a distinguished poet.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.66,1:44:01.65,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,能见到您这样的夫人是我的荣幸\N A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.67,1:44:05.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你有我的名片吗？\NYou have my card, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.67,1:44:10.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- Yes...Yes.   - Will you send the manuscripts to that address?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.67,1:44:10.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(532.429,440)}- 你会将手搞寄来吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.67,1:44:10.14,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(330,440)}- 是，是的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.47,1:44:13.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,- Of course.  - Please don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.47,1:44:13.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(355,440)}- 当然
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.47,1:44:13.68,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,{\pos(470,440)}- 请别忘记
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.68,1:44:17.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们一定慎重的去芜存菁\NAnd rest assured We shall make a very careful selection of what is to survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.68,1:44:20.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,再见\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.70,1:44:41.69,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,苦艾酒，两杯\NAbsinthe. Two.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.75,1:45:25.75,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,跟我说，你是否爱我\NTell me if you love me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.00,1:45:30.67,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你知道我很喜欢你\NYou know I'm very fond of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.14,1:45:37.60,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,你爱我吗？\NDo you love me?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.52,1:45:39.81,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,爱 \NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.76,1:45:42.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,那就把手放在桌上\NThen Put your hand on the table.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.76,1:45:43.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.76,1:45:43.98,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.35,1:45:46.73,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,把手放桌上\NPut your hand on the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.77,1:45:52.76,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,手心朝上\NPalm upwards.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.83,1:46:55.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,他死后，我夜夜见到他\NSince he died, I see him every night...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.38,1:46:59.83,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我的伟大和荣耀的罪\Nmy great and radiant sin.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.84,1:47:05.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我们一直很快乐……一直\NWe were always happy... always.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.85,1:47:07.84,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我都记得\NI remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.85,1:47:14.07,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,我找到了\NI found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.86,1:47:17.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.86,1:47:17.85,微软雅黑0 1 30,,25,0,15,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.86,1:47:20.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,永恒\NEternity.\N
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.86,1:47:24.87,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,就是太阳与海\NIt's the sun mingled...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.87,1:47:26.86,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,交相辉映\Nwith the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.88,1:47:46.88,微软雅黑0 1 30,,0,0,15,,剧终 谢谢观赏
